Comments: In this complex with TCX3C-ABCDE and with TCX3C-ABCD [PDB: 2Z93], the Fab's side chains facing the antigen fragments are almost identical in conformation and orientation, except for H-Asn58 .  In the CTX3C-ABCDE·10C9 Fab complex, a hydrogen bond between Of of CTX3C-ABCDE and H-Asn58-NH of 10C9 Fab creates a network of hydrogen bonds between H-Asn58, H-Tyr59, and L-Asn94.
